{"id": 57722, "date": "2025-07-14T04:00:11", "date_gmt": "2025-07-14T11:00:11", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57722"}, "modified": "2026-03-12T10:56:05", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-12T17:56:05", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-14-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/14/kingdom-of-days-july-14-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 14"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1974:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their third of three nights at The Bottom Line in New York City.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28267\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1974-0714-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1974-0714.jpg?fit=313%2C800&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"313,800\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1974-0714\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1974-0714.jpg?fit=117%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1974-0714.jpg?fit=313%2C800&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28267 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1974-0714.jpg?resize=313%2C800&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"313\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1974-0714.jpg?w=313&amp;ssl=1 313w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1974-0714.jpg?resize=117%2C300&amp;ssl=1 117w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 313px) 100vw, 313px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Bruce records vocal overdubs for &#8220;Jungleland&#8221; at the Record Plant in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band continue their Texas swing, as the Darkness Tour arrives for a night in San Antonio (Bruce&#8217;s one and only performance in that city). By request, Bruce tour premieres &#8220;The Fever.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-lOl367T5-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/lOl367T5?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19530\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-7-14/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-7-14.jpg?fit=1253%2C928&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1253,928\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1593430603&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-7-14\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-7-14.jpg?fit=300%2C222&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-7-14.jpg?fit=758%2C561&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19530 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-7-14.jpg?resize=758%2C561&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"561\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-7-14.jpg?w=1253&amp;ssl=1 1253w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-7-14.jpg?resize=300%2C222&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-7-14.jpg?resize=1024%2C758&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/1978-7-14.jpg?resize=768%2C569&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"2999\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-0714/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1978-0714.jpg?fit=577%2C1200&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"577,1200\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Picasa&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1335116522&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-0714\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1978-0714.jpg?fit=144%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1978-0714.jpg?fit=492%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-2999 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1978-0714.jpg?resize=577%2C1200&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"577\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1978-0714.jpg?w=577&amp;ssl=1 577w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1978-0714.jpg?resize=144%2C300&amp;ssl=1 144w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1978-0714.jpg?resize=492%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 492w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 577px) 100vw, 577px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>Nils Lofgren records his vocal and guitar overdubs for &#8220;Janey, Don&#8217;t You Lose Heart.&#8221; It will become his first appearance on an official Springsteen studio release.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kKIPdOVWTjU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1988:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band bring the Tunnel of Love Tour to St. Jakob Stadion in Basel, Switzerland. The show is filmed professionally and is a delight to watch. Check out the encores below, including the only performance of &#8220;Follow That Dream&#8221; on the tour.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/6h2V61SEBGg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5YXc0iIsoSU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/k_1pjf6Bre8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/e_YFj7xvcXw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/DsfZpMugrNk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLJTyL9twk3zDetAqZt3KJhnUUiIdH7T8w\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play a warm-up set for the first U.S. leg of the Reunion Tour at Continental Airlines Arena in East Rutherford.</p>\n<p><strong>2002:\u00a0</strong>The\u00a0<em>New York Times</em> publishes an article on Bruce&#8217;s upcoming album,\u00a0<em>The Rising,\u00a0</em>In his article, Jon Pareles quotes frequently from the interview he conducted with Bruce to inform it, but you can hear the interview itself below.</p>\n<div id=\"v-yHujCIf5-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/yHujCIf5?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>2005:\u00a0</strong>Bruce kicks off the encores at his solo acoustic show in Toronto with the tour premiere of &#8220;Darlington County.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Tq-Zp9idlVE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"68268\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/14/kingdom-of-days-july-14-2/screenshot-2026-03-12-105532/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Screenshot-2026-03-12-105532.jpg?fit=730%2C1654&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"730,1654\" data-comments-opened=\"0\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot 2026-03-12 105532\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Screenshot-2026-03-12-105532.jpg?fit=132%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Screenshot-2026-03-12-105532.jpg?fit=452%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-68268\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Screenshot-2026-03-12-105532.jpg?resize=730%2C1654&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"730\" height=\"1654\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Screenshot-2026-03-12-105532.jpg?w=730&amp;ssl=1 730w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Screenshot-2026-03-12-105532.jpg?resize=132%2C300&amp;ssl=1 132w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Screenshot-2026-03-12-105532.jpg?resize=452%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 452w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Screenshot-2026-03-12-105532.jpg?resize=678%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 678w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2009:\u00a0</strong>&#8220;Pink Cadillac&#8221; makes a welcome return after a six-year absence at Bruce&#8217;s Working on a Dream show in Glasgow&#8217;s Hampden Park.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Hf0lDibY8I8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2012:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band headline Hard Rock Calling in London&#8217;s Hyde Park on what will prove to be an eventful day, and a highly anticipated one:</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/eg3fySaCohI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>It starts with a surprise guest appearance by Bruce during John Fogerty&#8217;s set:</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/DyQ6mN2EhWY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>&#8230;and things pick up during Bruce&#8217;s set: Bruce and Roy open by themselves, playing &#8220;Thunder Road&#8221; like they did at Bruce&#8217;s legendary Hammersmith Odeon show in 1975.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/pvfFuASYgfM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>Guest appearances by Tom Morello and John Fogerty quickly follow, along with the tour premiere of the very rare &#8220;Take &#8216;Em as They Come.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/KQLmV1fCxt8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>But it&#8217;s the encore surprise that garners worldwide headlines, when Bruce invites Sir Paul McCartney to join him on stage for &#8220;I Saw Her Standing There&#8221; and &#8220;Twist and Shout.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SzhXSSRPvxQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>Unfortunately, and mystifyingly, the festival staff pull the plug on Bruce, Paul, and the band when they sail past their 10:30pm curfew. Unable to close the show in his customary fashion, Bruce merely sings a brief &#8220;Goodnight Irene&#8221; and exits. (The broadcast clip above ends before the power cut, but you can watch the unedited footage below to see how it played out.)</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dJ0SQ6NX13U?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>Over the days and weeks that follow, the incident will become legendary.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XO5wYdX28JM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Y5Mru2ZuYoA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/8kM2sw9LFsU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28271\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2012-07-14/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2012-07-14.jpg?fit=1514%2C2205&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1514,2205\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2012-07-14\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2012-07-14.jpg?fit=206%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2012-07-14.jpg?fit=703%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28271 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2012-07-14.jpg?resize=758%2C1104&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1104\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2012-07-14.jpg?w=1514&amp;ssl=1 1514w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2012-07-14.jpg?resize=206%2C300&amp;ssl=1 206w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2012-07-14.jpg?resize=703%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 703w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2012-07-14.jpg?resize=768%2C1119&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2012-07-14.jpg?resize=1055%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1055w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2012-07-14.jpg?resize=1406%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 1406w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>2021:\u00a0</strong>BBC Radio 2 airs Zoe Ball&#8217;s interview with Bruce, while in New York City\u00a0<em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its limited return engagement at The St. James Theater. In attendance tonight: Garry Tallent.</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-57722-7\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/The-Zoe-Ball-Breakfast-Show-Bruce-Springsteen-BBC-Sounds-Springsteen-Only.mp3?_=7\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/The-Zoe-Ball-Breakfast-Show-Bruce-Springsteen-BBC-Sounds-Springsteen-Only.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/The-Zoe-Ball-Breakfast-Show-Bruce-Springsteen-BBC-Sounds-Springsteen-Only.mp3</a></audio>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>On this date: Bruce and Paul McCartney learn what happens when you break curfew at Hyde Park.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 19532, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}}, "categories": [2], "tags": [1272, 872, 424, 508,